  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To combat post-transplant weight gain, we seek to expand Stanford Kidney Transplant's
      multidisciplinary platform to include physical activity monitoring and coaching using the
      Apple Watch.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
